"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-golf-news-denied-spot-in-paris-by-dutch-olympic-committee-dewi-weber-leads-portland-classic\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PORTLAND, Ore. (AP) Denied a spot in Paris because the Dutch Olympic committee did not think she was good enough to contend, Dewi Weber shot a 10-under 62 on Friday to take the second-round lead in the Portland Classic.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999149741994394, \"rank\": 8.503302940450506e-05, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 37, \"end\": 42, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999472493, \"rank\": 5.2633595392119035e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 55, \"end\": 78, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.0693066050164846e-12, \"text\": \"Dutch Olympic committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\"}, {\"begin\": 125, \"end\": 135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dewi_Weber\", \"score\": 0.9999997042137221, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dewi Weber\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dewi_Weber\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dewi_Weber\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Weber qualified for the Olympics under International Golf Federation standards, but was left out because of the country's separate standards for all sports to meet a realistic chance of a top-eight finish.\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are two rounds in, so we will see how this all unfolds and if I can really make a statement,\\\" Weber said.\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 526, \"end\": 531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Maria_von_Weber\", \"score\": 0.9376584155089142, \"rank\": 0.06472956698066647, \"text\": \"Weber\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Maria_von_Weber\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Maria_von_Weber\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Of course it's in the back of my mind because it's the week before the Olympics.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was something that I was looking forward to.\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 667, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"...  \\\"It sucks, but all we can do is like try to prove why those standards were so silly, and I really hope to do that on Sunday.\\\"\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 798, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Playing only her second LPGA Tour event of the year, Weber had nine birdies in an 11-hole stretch in her afternoon round at Columbia Edgewater, making seven birdies in a row on Nos.\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 824, \"end\": 828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LPGA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LPGA\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LPGA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LPGA\"}, {\"begin\": 853, \"end\": 858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Maria_von_Weber\", \"score\": 0.9376584155089142, \"rank\": 0.06472956698066647, \"text\": \"Weber\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Maria_von_Weber\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Maria_von_Weber\"}, {\"begin\": 924, \"end\": 942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Columbia_Edgewater_Country_Club\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Columbia Edgewater\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Columbia_Edgewater_Country_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Columbia_Edgewater_Country_Club\"}, {\"begin\": 977, \"end\": 980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nederlandse_Omroep_Stichting\", \"score\": 0.999999655696288, \"rank\": 3.4429899597644496e-07, \"text\": \"Nos\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nederlandse_Omroep_Stichting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nederlandse_Omroep_Stichting\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"5-11.\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 987, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She closed with a birdie on the par-4 18th for a two-shot lead over first-round leader Polly Mack and past champion Andrea Lee.\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1075, \"end\": 1080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polly_Plummer\", \"score\": 0.9823703768561042, \"rank\": 0.015072144637334533, \"text\": \"Polly\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polly_Plummer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polly_Plummer\"}, {\"begin\": 1081, \"end\": 1085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelvin_Mack\", \"score\": 0.7797879473670384, \"rank\": 0.2760893350750266, \"text\": \"Mack\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelvin_Mack\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelvin_Mack\"}, {\"begin\": 1104, \"end\": 1114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Lee_(fighter)\", \"score\": 0.7753296322737864, \"rank\": 0.1534090909090328, \"text\": \"Andrea Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Lee_(fighter)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Lee_(fighter)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Very easy, very relaxing, not really putting my pressure on myself,\\\" Weber said.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1198, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1187, \"end\": 1192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Maria_von_Weber\", \"score\": 0.9376584155089142, \"rank\": 0.06472956698066647, \"text\": \"Weber\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Maria_von_Weber\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Maria_von_Weber\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Just like roll that ball as well as I can and see what happens.\\\"\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1264, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 28-year-old former Miami player also had seven straight birdies Thursday in an opening 66.\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1289, \"end\": 1294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami_Hurricanes_football\", \"score\": 0.9047015874682848, \"rank\": 0.10530832987946838, \"text\": \"Miami\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami_Hurricanes_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami_Hurricanes_football\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She the final eight holes Thursday and the first 13 Friday in 16 under - and was 16 under overall for 36 holes in pursuit of her first LPGA Tour title.\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1496, \"end\": 1500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LPGA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LPGA\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LPGA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LPGA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did a really good job both days of just going shot for shot, which I know is such a cliche but I have never been able to really do that,\\\" said Weber, who has four top-seven finishes in 11 starts this year on the Epson Tour.\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1660, \"end\": 1665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Maria_von_Weber\", \"score\": 0.9376584155089142, \"rank\": 0.06472956698066647, \"text\": \"Weber\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Maria_von_Weber\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Maria_von_Weber\"}, {\"begin\": 1729, \"end\": 1739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epson_Tour\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Epson Tour\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epson_Tour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epson_Tour\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mack followed her opening 63 with a 67 in the afternoon.\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1798, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 25-year-old German also is winless on the LPGA Tour.\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1815, \"end\": 1821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.9130657641539874, \"rank\": 0.08847408303134567, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1845, \"end\": 1849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LPGA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LPGA\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LPGA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LPGA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She eagled the par-5 seventh, and and dropped back with a bogey on the par-4 15th.\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1938, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You obviously want to do well after that round, but it's still not the easiest golf course,\\\" Mack said.\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 2044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2034, \"end\": 2038, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelvin_Mack\", \"score\": 0.7797879473670384, \"rank\": 0.2760893350750266, \"text\": \"Mack\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelvin_Mack\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelvin_Mack\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's still a golf course.\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's still 18 holes to get through it.\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2110, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I did pretty well.\\\"\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2138, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lee shot 63 in the morning, running off six straight birdies of her own in a back-nine burst.\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2233, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2140, \"end\": 2143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9999998209591627, \"rank\": 1.09647802566615e-07, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 25-year-old American won the 2022 event for her lone LPGA Tour title.\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2250, \"end\": 2258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998535033651997, \"rank\": 0.00010571421740158828, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2291, \"end\": 2295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LPGA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LPGA\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LPGA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LPGA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love Portland, Columbia Edgewater,\\\" Lee said.\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2357, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2327, \"end\": 2345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Columbia_Edgewater_Country_Club\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Columbia Edgewater\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Columbia_Edgewater_Country_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://db