: \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Talley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lauren Coughlin, who won her first LPGA Tour title at the CPKC Women's Open on Sunday in Calgary, Alberta, was 9 under after a 69.\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2700, \"end\": 2704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LPGA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LPGA\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LPGA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LPGA\"}, {\"begin\": 2754, \"end\": 2761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calgary\", \"score\": 0.999649995541878, \"rank\": 0.0003267788670880004, \"text\": \"Calgary\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calgary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calgary\"}, {\"begin\": 2763, \"end\": 2770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alberta\", \"score\": 0.6875932815057145, \"rank\": 0.4542891420837575, \"text\": \"Alberta\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alberta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alberta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the Olympics next week, no one from the top 30 in the world ranking is in the field.\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2886, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The lone Olympian in the field is Aditi Ashok of India.\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2896, \"end\": 2904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999994293763657, \"rank\": 5.706227836542216e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 2921, \"end\": 2932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aditi_Ashok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aditi Ashok\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aditi_As